Thanks to our good relations, the <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> has offered a compromise that raises some taxes on the wealthy, along with lesser welfare cuts. Our members have mixed opinions on accepting this compromise. The Liberals support maintaining our government to keep the fascists and communists out, while Labor supports the compromise in the hopes of moderating the pain of the workers they represent, but the Industrialists who provide the bulk of the funding our party needs to function are strongly opposed. The nationalists, of course, oppose it as capitulation to the <span style="color: #E3000F;">**socialists**</span>.

- @accept_compromise: Accept the compromise.
- @destroy: Reject the compromise and let this government fall.

